      "text": "Let me offer some further notes on the plot basis I mailed you for my book: I am more and more convinced that all mystery deities from Dionysos to the Christos were/was the same. That he resurrected the dead or sleeping man the way the forces of spring/nature revive all sleeping roots, bulbs, trees, etc.; all nature which is not man, and that the cyclic small year is to nature in general as the great year (200 B.C. to 2000 AD) is to the species man. Therefore, in my novel, TO SCARE THE DEAD, if ",
