    },
    {
      "text": "UBIK does indeed to resemble Dr. NK's time theory that one knowing his time theory could not escape noticing this when he read UBIK (for example, the scientific explanation of Ubik assigns a positive value, in terms of life-sustaining or giving energy, to a counterclock spin, which is virtually a parody of Dr. NK's concept of lefthandedness being life supportive). This would bring UBIK to their attention (as it later brought Dr. NK's theory to my attention). But in no way, probably, was I influe",
